### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@maragataId = be9e1c72-6c27-438e-9deb-6ef0207c365a

### ========================================
### DEVICE ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### 1. Post device (PUBLIC - No auth required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{maragataId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fcmToken": "your_fcm_token_here"
}

### 2. Send push notification to ALL devices of a station
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{maragataId}}/notify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "17.54",
  "body": "Hoy tenemos un programa especial en vivo. ¡No te lo pierdas!",
  "image": "https://firebase.google.com/static/images/brand-guidelines/logo-monochrome.png",
  "data": {
    "screen": "live",
    "programId": "abc123",
    "action": "open_player"
  }
}